  "detailed_description": "<h1>FEATURES</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Minimalist </strong>Art Style</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A short game intended to be finished in <strong>under an hour</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A <strong>variety</strong> of environments and possible experiences</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Casual Gameplay</strong> with no skill-based mechanics</li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957220/extras/22771dde2c48274d2ad5b1f9d56745e4.poster.avif?t=1654546664\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957220/extras/22771dde2c48274d2ad5b1f9d56745e4.webm?t=1654546664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957220/extras/22771dde2c48274d2ad5b1f9d56745e4.mp4?t=1654546664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>TIMEOUT.</strong><br>A dreaded prospect on a <strong>cold</strong> and <strong>rainy</strong> night. The toys scattered around the room are sure to help you pass the time. <br><br>Journey to faraway lands, through the power of your <strong>imagination</strong>. Discover lost knowledge and keep an eye out for the elusive clue here and there.<br><br>Use your inquisitive nature to find solutions and secrets that can help you on your quest to crack the door's <u>five</u> locks and be free of your <strong>confinement</strong> in this simple, yet unorthodox, adventure, puzzle solver.",
